narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: More work than L3, but worth it

Spanish 140 is WAY better than the first three semesters. You speak a ton in class and get to actually apply the grammar that you've been learning. It is not horribly difficult, but is a great class if you actually care about Spanish. I would highly recommend professor Len, who is a skilled and super helpful teacher.
I would recommend this class to another student because it helped improve my Spanish and was fun.
You learn a lot of grammar stuff. There's more focus on speaking in L4 than L3, but you do get better at speaking.
I would absolutely recommend this class.
